#~ msgid "There are always flowers <br/>for those who want to see them."
#~ msgstr "Sempre hi ha flors <br/>per a aquells que volem veure-les."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To do so, we collaborate with local producers who care about the "
#~ "environment and cultivate their flowers with love."
